On the ground floor there are shops, while first floor is the proper mosque. Quite a number of devotees come here for prayers.

Needs more attention on cleanliness front.

featured_reviews.review_translated_text: Friends, Rohtak's Lal Masjid, Fort Road, Railway Road, Bhiwani Stand (Bhiwani octroi is different). 'Sheori Market' Durga Bhawan Temple all these are situated at one place in Rohtak. From the railway station you will reach here in just 5 minutes on foot. From Rohtak Old Bus Stand you can reach there on foot in 10-15 minutes or you can take an auto which charges Rs 15. To reach here from Rohtak New Bus Stand, you will have to take an auto because it is located at a long distance from here. Friends, this is the busiest place in the city. Earlier there was no space for parking here but now parking has been made.
